1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,182
=Episode 19=

12
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:55,140
You are finally back.

13
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,259
News came from the palace.

14
00:00:56,260 --> 00:00:57,739
Tonight, Lords Xiang and He

15
00:00:57,740 --> 00:00:59,340
were both attacked.

16
00:00:59,860 --> 00:01:00,779
Are you unharmed?

17
00:01:00,780 --> 00:01:01,979
I was at the Ministry of War.

18
00:01:01,980 --> 00:01:03,140
Let me see.

19
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:09,460
You frightened me to death.

20
00:01:13,140 --> 00:01:14,740
I was talking about serious matters.

21
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:18,080
I was more worried about you alone
at the Grand Princess's Residence.

22
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:20,100
Your safety matters most.

23
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:32,060
Grand Princess.

24
00:01:33,980 --> 00:01:35,100
Wuju.

25
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:37,020
Grand Princess.

26
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:40,220
Wuju.

27
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:42,180
Grand Princess.

28
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:45,899
Grand Princess.

29
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:47,660
What were you dreaming about?

30
00:01:55,050 --> 00:01:57,379
(Twelve years ago
Year Twenty of Chengshun Reign)

31
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:58,179
Boss.

32
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,260
A bowl of noodles.

33
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,620
Coming right up.

34
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:06,420
Here you go.

35
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:09,820
Your noodles.

36
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:11,860
Boss.

37
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:13,659
Boss.

38
00:02:13,660 --> 00:02:14,620
Yes?

39
00:02:14,820 --> 00:02:17,180
Why is the street so empty?

40
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:19,260
There is a challenge match over there.

41
00:02:19,460 --> 00:02:21,100
They are choosing
the Top Martial Champion.

42
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:24,140
Whoever wins

43
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:25,339
will become

44
00:02:25,340 --> 00:02:28,020
the Grand Princess's Prince Consort.

45
00:02:28,140 --> 00:02:30,459
The whole city has gone to watch.

46
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,780
It is quite lively.

47
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:34,620
Enjoy.

48
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,340
Please enjoy.

49
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,339
Just a brute with fists.

50
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,940
What is there to see?

51
00:02:44,975 --> 00:02:45,979
Brother,

52
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:46,979
my name is Sun Gong.

53
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:48,419
I have just arrived in the Capital.

54
00:02:48,420 --> 00:02:50,099
I have spent all my money.

55
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:52,540
May I trouble you for a bowl of noodles?

56
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:59,260
The owner is gone. No more food.

57
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:01,179
If you do not mind,

58
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:03,019
we can share one bowl.

59
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:04,060
All right.

60
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:06,459
I truly am starving.

61
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:07,900
Please do not take offense.

62
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:13,979
It is fine.

63
00:03:13,980 --> 00:03:16,660
Those who walk the martial world
all need help at times.

64
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:17,980
You may have it all.

65
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:23,180
Brother, you are not interested in that?

66
00:03:23,860 --> 00:03:25,259
I am here to enter the contest.

67
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:26,219
That is why I shamelessly

68
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:27,820
asked you for a meal.

69
00:03:29,140 --> 00:03:30,499
Someone like you

70
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:31,780
plans to fight on the platform?

71
00:03:32,420 --> 00:03:33,980
To compete for Top Martial Champion?

72
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:36,059
Then stop dividing it.

73
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:37,180
Eat up.

74
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:39,339
No need to worry.

75
00:03:39,340 --> 00:03:40,540
Do not be nervous.

76
00:03:41,340 --> 00:03:44,340
Are you confident about winning?

77
00:03:44,380 --> 00:03:47,500
One should not boast
of what is yet undone.

78
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:51,540
Stop splitting it.

79
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:53,420
It will get cold.

80
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:55,219
Whoever reaches the middle

81
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:56,820
can bite it off.

82
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,940
Then I shall not stand on ceremony.

83
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:12,339
All my life, I have admired
Zhong Wuyan, Hua Mulan,

84
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:14,099
and Mu Guiying, heroes among women.

85
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:15,379
If I offended you just now,

86
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:16,500
I ask

87
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:18,580
for your understanding.

88
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:25,380
No need to mind it.

89
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:28,060
Our dynasty has such women as well.

90
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:30,339
That would be the one
who once shook the borders,

91
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:31,579
leader of the Xiao Army,

92
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:33,580
Xiao Congrong.

93
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:42,540
Thank you, Young Master Sun,

94
00:04:42,900 --> 00:04:44,340
for not exposing me.

95
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:50,859
Young Master Sun,

96
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:52,419
did you enter the martial exam

97
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:53,980
without telling your family?

98
00:04:54,940 --> 00:04:56,339
I have no family.

99
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:58,540
My parents and brothers
all died of plague,

100
00:04:58,740 --> 00:05:00,780
leaving me alone in this world.

101
00:05:06,312 --> 00:05:08,420
Then you must win the title
of Top Martial Champion.

102
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:10,380
I will wait for you in the palace.

103
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:23,020
Summon Top Martial Champion
Sun Gong to enter.

104
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:29,220
This way, please.

105
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:37,580
Please wait here.

106
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:45,340
(Father.)

107
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:47,100
(Mother.)

108
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,500
(I have come to the palace again.)

109
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:52,700
(Only...)

110
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:56,260
(I am no longer who I was.)

111
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,220
It is you.

112
00:06:21,820 --> 00:06:22,619
What?

113
00:06:22,620 --> 00:06:24,499
Are you disappointed to see me,

114
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:25,620
Prince Consort?

115
00:06:28,660 --> 00:06:32,540
(The Grand Princess... It is her.)

116
00:06:40,187 --> 00:06:43,900
The Grand Princess is choosing
a Prince Consort through the martial exam.

117
00:06:43,962 --> 00:06:46,282
This is your perfect chance.

118
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:52,020
She can secure your footing
in the royal house quickly.

119
00:06:57,820 --> 00:06:59,660
Win her trust.

120
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:03,100
Take control of the military
as soon as possible.

121
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:06,620
That foolish emperor deserves to die.

122
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:09,660
Along with his kin and ministers,

123
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:14,220
only then will it honor
your parents and the Zhen clan.

124
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:15,660
Uncle,

125
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:18,980
I will avenge my parents at any cost.

126
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:20,499
But before that,

127
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:22,059
I ask one thing of you.

128
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:23,180
Speak.

129
00:07:24,180 --> 00:07:25,900
Help me find a medicine,

130
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:28,660
a birth-control tea taken
after intimacy, that leaves no offspring.

131
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,780
Since this is a cursed bond,

132
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:35,020
I don't want it
to leave anything behind.

133
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:45,100
Remember this.

134
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:47,580
Take it on the fifteenth of each month.

135
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:48,459
Once you do,

136
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:50,980
there will be no turning back.

137
00:07:56,020 --> 00:07:57,140
Prince Consort,

138
00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:01,660
from today on, we are husband and wife.

139
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:05,020
I have a secret to tell you.

140
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:08,700
Before this,

141
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:11,340
I had been waiting for someone.

142
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:13,300
His name was Zhen Muyu.

143
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:14,860
I know.

144
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:18,700
Years ago, Your Highness
declared you would marry him.

145
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:20,860
The whole realm knew of it.

146
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:23,140
Yes.

147
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:28,220
The day the Zhen Residence
was condemned, he vanished.

148
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:31,140
I have waited all these years.

149
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:33,740
Yet there has been no word of him.

150
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:35,380
Alive or dead, I do not know.

151
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:37,499
I never even saw

152
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,340
what he looked like grown.

153
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:42,900
My imperial brother
ordered me to stop waiting.

154
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:45,300
If I waited longer, I would grow old.

155
00:08:46,420 --> 00:08:47,540
I suppose

156
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:51,460
we were fated to miss each other.

157
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:56,300
Why are you telling me this?

158
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:02,060
Before the veil is lifted,

159
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:04,340
I wanted to be honest with you.

160
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:11,620
Since the day of the martial exam
when I met you,

161
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:15,580
I decided to stop waiting for him.

162
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:19,980
Because I found my own fate.

163
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:39,020
What is wrong?

164
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:40,979
Nothing.

165
00:09:40,980 --> 00:09:43,300
I was just moved by what you said.

166
00:10:07,300 --> 00:10:08,420
From that moment on,

167
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:10,940
I no longer cared who Zhen Muyu was,

168
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:14,540
only how good Sun Gong was to me.

169
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:22,020
(Princess.)

170
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:24,939
(You've seen what Zhen Muyu)

171
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:26,380
(looks like as an adult.)

172
00:10:26,980 --> 00:10:28,100
(Only...)

173
00:10:29,220 --> 00:10:30,740
(One day,)

174
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:34,540
(he will shatter your sincere heart.)
